main_body:
Under the 268th partial invitation to tender opened pursuant to Regulation (EEC) No 1627/89:
(a) for category A:
- the maximum buying-in price shall be EUR 226,00/100 kg of carcasses or half-carcasses of quality R3,
- the maximum quantity of carcasses, half-carcasses, and forequarters accepted shall be 8597,5 t;
(b) for category C no award shall be made;
(c) for carcasses and half-carcasses of store cattle as referred to in Article 1(7) of Regulation (EC) No 590/2001, no award shall be made.
